with cte as(
SELECT * FROM(
SELECT DISTINCT *
FROM `temp.pogNM_bauNewFile` 
)p

JOIN(
    SELECT *
    FROM `temp.FB_Live_NewFeed`
    where availability='in stock') fb
ON p.pog = fb.dmPublisherInfoId
where lower(fb.customLabel2) like '%cpt1%')

SELECT  CASE WHEN  bau_nm3 BETWEEN -40 AND 0 THEN 'NEG40_0NM'
        WHEN bau_nm3 BETWEEN 0 AND 16 THEN '0_16NM'
        WHEN bau_nm3 BETWEEN 16.5 AND 21 THEN '16_21NM'
        ELSE NULL END AS NM
        ,COUNT(DISTINCT pog) As Pogs 
                                           
   FROM cte
   
   GROUP BY CASE WHEN  bau_nm3 BETWEEN -40 AND 0 THEN 'NEG40_0NM'
        WHEN bau_nm3 BETWEEN 0 AND 16 THEN '0_16NM'
        WHEN bau_nm3 BETWEEN 16.5 AND 21 THEN '16_21NM'
        ELSE NULL END
   
  
",1000)
